sentences: Anniela (born 3 June 1990) is a Swedish pop singer originally from Rinkaby in Skåne,
but has been living in Stockholm for a few years.
released her début album Extravaganza in 2009.
she was 13 years old and in various musicals.
In 2011 she participated in Melodifestivalen 2011 with the song Elektrisk, with lyrics in Swedish, which is a first for her.
